GC.XPN.COMP.CN-fs.def: Compensation of employees consists of all payments in cash, as well as in kind (such as food and housing), to employees in return for services rendered, and government contributions to social insurance schemes such as social security and pensions that provide benefits to employees.
GC.XPN.COMP.CN-fs.name: Compensation of employees
GC.XPN.COMP.CN-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.COMP.ZS-fs.def: Compensation of employees consists of all payments in cash, as well as in kind (such as food and housing), to employees in return for services rendered, and government contributions to social insurance schemes such as social security and pensions that provide benefits to employees.
GC.XPN.COMP.ZS-fs.name: Compensation of employees
GC.XPN.COMP.ZS-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.GSRV.CN-fs.def: Goods and services include all government payments in exchange for goods and services used for the production of market and nonmarket goods and services. Own-account capital formation is excluded.
GC.XPN.GSRV.CN-fs.name: Goods and services expense
GC.XPN.GSRV.CN-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.GSRV.ZS-fs.def: Goods and services include all government payments in exchange for goods and services used for the production of market and nonmarket goods and services. Own-account capital formation is excluded.
GC.XPN.GSRV.ZS-fs.name: Goods and services expense
GC.XPN.GSRV.ZS-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.INTP.CN-fs.def: Interest payments include interest payments on government debt--including long-term bonds, long-term loans, and other debt instruments--to domestic and foreign residents.
GC.XPN.INTP.CN-fs.name: Interest payments
GC.XPN.INTP.CN-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.INTP.RV.ZS-fs.def: Interest payments include interest payments on government debt--including long-term bonds, long-term loans, and other debt instruments--to domestic and foreign residents.
GC.XPN.INTP.RV.ZS-fs.name: Interest payments
GC.XPN.INTP.RV.ZS-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.INTP.ZS-fs.def: Interest payments include interest payments on government debt--including long-term bonds, long-term loans, and other debt instruments--to domestic and foreign residents.
GC.XPN.INTP.ZS-fs.name: Interest payments
GC.XPN.INTP.ZS-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.OTHR.CN-fs.def: Other expense is spending on dividends, rent, and other miscellaneous expenses, including provision for consumption of fixed capital.
GC.XPN.OTHR.CN-fs.name: Other expense
GC.XPN.OTHR.CN-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.OTHR.ZS-fs.def: Other expense is spending on dividends, rent, and other miscellaneous expenses, including provision for consumption of fixed capital.
GC.XPN.OTHR.ZS-fs.name: Other expense
GC.XPN.OTHR.ZS-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.TOTL.CN-fs.def: Expense is cash payments for operating activities of the government in providing goods and services. It includes compensation of employees (such as wages and salaries), interest and subsidies, grants, social benefits, and other expenses such as rent and dividends.
GC.XPN.TOTL.CN-fs.name: Expense
GC.XPN.TOTL.CN-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.TOTL.GD.ZS-fs.def: Expense is cash payments for operating activities of the government in providing goods and services. It includes compensation of employees (such as wages and salaries), interest and subsidies, grants, social benefits, and other expenses such as rent and dividends.
GC.XPN.TOTL.GD.ZS-fs.name: Expense
GC.XPN.TOTL.GD.ZS-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files, and World Bank and OECD GDP estimates.

GC.XPN.TRFT.CN-fs.def: Subsidies, grants, and other social benefits include all unrequited, nonrepayable transfers on current account to private and public enterprises; grants to foreign governments, international organizations, and other government units; and social security, social assistance benefits, and employer social benefits in cash and in kind.
GC.XPN.TRFT.CN-fs.name: Subsidies and other transfers
GC.XPN.TRFT.CN-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.

GC.XPN.TRFT.ZS-fs.def: Subsidies, grants, and other social benefits include all unrequited, nonrepayable transfers on current account to private and public enterprises; grants to foreign governments, international organizations, and other government units; and social security, social assistance benefits, and employer social benefits in cash and in kind.
GC.XPN.TRFT.ZS-fs.name: Subsidies and other transfers
GC.XPN.TRFT.ZS-fs.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.
